Question:
https://leetcode.com/problems/swap-salary/


Topic: Case and one liner logical assignment


CODE 1 : The code is similar to expressions we use in c++ like ()?:

update salary
    set sex= IF(sex="m" , "f" , "m");
    
    
    
CODE 2: use case

Example:
CASE
    WHEN condition1 THEN result1
    WHEN condition2 THEN result2
    WHEN conditionN THEN resultN
    ELSE result
END; 


Code:
update salary
    set sex= case sex
        when 'm' then 'f'
        else 'm'
    end

